Raees -LRB- English : Wealthy -RRB- is a 2017 Indian action crime thriller film directed by Rahul Dholakia and produced by Gauri Khan , Ritesh Sidhwani and Farhan Akhtar under their banners Red Chillies Entertainment and Excel Entertainment .
It stars Shah Rukh Khan , Mahira Khan and Nawazuddin Siddiqui .
Raees was said to be based on criminal Abdul Latif 's life but , the filmmakers denied this , saying `` The story of the film is a pure work of fiction , not based on any person ; living or dead . ''
The film was released on 25 January 2017 .